nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE STRENGTHENS SOME FAR TO THE EAST-SOUTHEAST OF HAWAII...
summary: ...HENRIETTE STRENGTHENS SOME FAR TO THE EAST-SOUTHEAST OF HAWAII... As of 5:00 PM HST Mon Aug 04 the center of Henriette was located near 15.4, -121.9 with movement WNW at 15 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
